def Domenico(x,y,z,t,tau,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0):
    
    fx = exp(x/(2.0*alphaX)*(1.0-(1+4.0*k*alphaX/v)**0.5))* \
    erfc((x-v*t*(1.0+4.0*k*alphaX/v)**0.5)/(2.0*(alphaX*v*t)**0.5))+ \
    exp(x/(2.0*alphaX)*(1.0+(1+4.0*k*alphaX/v)**0.5))* \
    erfc((x+v*t*(1.0+4.0*k*alphaX/v)**0.5)/(2.0*(alphaX*v*t)**0.5))
    
    fy = erf((y+(Y0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaY*tau)**0.5))-erf((y-(Y0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaY*tau)**0.5))
    
    fz = erf((z+(Z0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaZ*tau)**0.5))-erf((z-(Z0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaZ*tau)**0.5))
    
    return c0/8.0*fx*fy*fz
In [4]:
def callTau(x,v,t,alphaX):
    
    n = (v*t/alphaX)**0.25
    
    return (x/v)/(1+(x/(v*t))**n)**(1/n)
In [5]:
def sub_wexler(x,y,z,t,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0,tau):
    
        fX = (x/(pi*v*alphaX)**0.5*exp(x/(2.0*alphaX))*
              exp(-v*tau/(4.0*alphaX)-k*tau-x**2.0/(4.0*v*alphaX*tau))/tau**(3.0/2.0))

        fY = erf((y+(Y0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaY*tau)**0.5)) - erf((y-(Y0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaY*tau)**0.5))

        fZ = erf((z+(Z0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaZ*tau)**0.5)) - erf((z-(Z0/2.0))/(2.0*(v*alphaZ*tau)**0.5))

        fWexler = c0/8*fX*fY*fZ
        
        return fWexler
    
def wexler(x,y,z,t,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0):
    
    intergral = integrate.quad(sub_wexler,0,t,args=(x,y,z,t,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0))[0]
    
    return intergral
In [6]:
# Model parameters
alphaX = 42.58     # Dispersion coeff in X-direction [m]
alphaY = 8.4310    # Dispersion coeff in Y-direction [m]
alphaZ = 0.00642   # Dispersion coeff in Z-direction [m]
v = 0.2151         # Velocity in x direction [m day-1]
Y0 = 240.0         # Source width in y direction [m]
Z0 = 5.0           # Source width in z direction [m]
c0 = 850.0         # Initial source concentration [mg L-1]
k = 0.00           # First order deacay constant [day-1]
tMax = 5110 # Simulation time [day]
xMax = 3000
yMax = 1500
zMax = 25
In [7]:
deltaT = tMax
deltaX = xMax/50
deltaY = yMax/50
deltaZ = zMax/50
t = np.arange(deltaT,tMax+deltaT,deltaT)
x = np.arange(0.01,xMax,deltaX)
y = np.arange(0,yMax+deltaY,deltaY)
z = np.arange(0,zMax+deltaZ,deltaZ)

Contour Plot in X-Y Plane¶

In [8]:
start = time.time()
Domenico_xy = np.zeros((len(x),len(y)))

for xi in range(0,len(x)):
    for yi in range(0,len(y)):
        Domenico_xy[xi,yi] = Domenico(x[xi],y[yi],1,tMax,x[xi]/v,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0)
        
end = time.time()

print("Runtime of the cell:",np.round(end-start,3))

Runtime of the cell: 0.026
In [20]:
contours = [450,300,100,10,1,0.1,0.01,0.001,0.0001][::-1]
[X, Y] = np.meshgrid(range(len(x)),range(len(y)))
Z = Domenico_xy[X,Y]

plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
ax = plt.gca() 
ax.set_aspect(1)

CS = plt.contour(x,y,Z,contours,colors='b',linestyles = 'dashed')
CLS = plt.clabel(CS, inline=1, fontsize=10)

plt.xlabel('X-axis',size=15)
plt.ylabel('Y-axis',size=15)

plt.title('Domenico plot for X-Y plane',size=18)
plt.show();

start = time.time()
Domenico_xy_tau = np.zeros((len(x),len(y)))

        Tau = callTau(x[xi],v,tMax,alphaX)
        Domenico_xy_tau[xi,yi] = Domenico(x[xi],y[yi],1,tMax,Tau,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0)
        
end = time.time()

print("Runtime of the cell:",np.round(end-start,3))

def demo(alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,v,Y0,Z0,c0,k,tMax,xMax,yMax,zMax):      

    deltaT = tMax
    deltaX = xMax/50
    deltaY = yMax/50
    deltaZ = zMax/50
    x = np.arange(0.01,xMax,deltaX)
    y = np.arange(0,yMax+deltaY,deltaY)
    Domenico_xy = np.zeros((len(x),len(y)))
    Domenico_xz = np.zeros((len(x),len(z)))
    

    for xi in range(0,len(x)):
        for yi in range(0,len(y)):
            Domenico_xy[xi,yi] = Domenico(x[xi],y[yi],1,tMax,x[xi]/v,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0)
    
    for xi in range(0,len(x)):
        for zi in range(0,len(z)):
            Domenico_xz[xi,zi] = Domenico(x[xi],0,z[zi],tMax,x[xi]/v,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0)
    
            
    contours = [450,300,100,10,1,0.1,0.01,0.001,0.0001][::-1]
    [X_xy, Y_xy] = np.meshgrid(range(len(x)),range(len(y)))
    Z_xy = Domenico_xy[X_xy,Y_xy]

    plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
    CS = plt.contour(x,y,Z_xy,contours)
    CLS = plt.clabel(CS, inline=1, fontsize=10)
    plt.xlabel('X-axis',size=15)
    plt.ylabel('Y-axis',size=15)
    plt.title('Domenico plot for X-Y plane',size=18)
    plt.show()
    
    
    [X_xz, Z_xz] = np.meshgrid(range(len(x)),range(len(z)))
    Y_xz = Domenico_xz[X_xz,Z_xz]

    plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
    CS = plt.contour(x,z,Y_xz,contours)
    CLS = plt.clabel(CS, inline=1, fontsize=10)
    plt.xlabel('X-axis',size=15)
    plt.ylabel('Z-axis',size=15)
    plt.title('Domenico plot for X-Z plane',size=18)
    plt.show()
    
    
interactive_plot = interactive(demo, alphaX = alphaX, alphaY = alphaY, alphaZ = alphaZ, v = v ,Y0 = Y0,Z0 = Z0, 
                         c0 = c0, k = k, tMax = tMax, xMax = xMax, yMax = yMax, zMax = zMax)
output = interactive_plot.children[-1]
output.layout.height = '1100px'
interactive_plot

def demo(alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,v,Y0,Z0,c0,k,tMax,xMax,yMax,zMax):      

    deltaT = tMax
    deltaX = xMax/50
    deltaY = yMax/50
    deltaZ = zMax/50
    x = np.arange(0.01,xMax,deltaX)
    y = np.arange(0,yMax+deltaY,deltaY)
    Domenico_xy = np.zeros((len(x),len(y)))
    Domenico_xz = np.zeros((len(x),len(z)))
    

    for xi in range(0,len(x)):
        for yi in range(0,len(y)):
            Domenico_xy[xi,yi] = Domenico(x[xi],y[yi],1,tMax,x[xi]/v,v,alphaX,alphaY,alphaZ,k,Y0,Z0,c0)
            
    contours = [450,300,100,10,1,0.1,0.01,0.001,0.0001][::-1]
    [X_xy, Y_xy] = np.meshgrid(range(len(x)),range(len(y)))
    Z_xy = Domenico_xy[X_xy,Y_xy]

    plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
    CS = plt.contour(x,y,Z_xy,contours)
    CLS = plt.clabel(CS, inline=1, fontsize=10)
    plt.xlabel('X-axis',size=15)
    plt.ylabel('Y-axis',size=15)
    plt.title('Domenico plot for X-Y plane',size=18)
    plt.show()
    
out = interactive(demo, alphaX = alphaX, alphaY = alphaY, alphaZ = alphaZ, v = v ,Y0 = Y0,Z0 = Z0, 
                         c0 = c0, k = k, tMax = tMax, xMax = xMax, yMax = yMax, zMax = zMax)
output = out.children[-1]
output.layout.height = '700px'
